oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Steep Canyon Rangers Appearances
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Steep Canyon Rangers (Musical group); Bluegrass music; Woodcuts (prints); Musical instruments; Guitar;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and black on white) announcing the Steep Canyon Rangers live at the Boulder Theater on January 23, Rllinsville Stage Stop on January 24, Paradise Theater on January 25, and Henry Strater Theater on January 26. Poster features woodcuts of guitars and roosters.
